Yetunde Arobieke (amụrụ na Mee 6, 1960) bụ onye kọmishọna ugbu a maka Gọọmentị Obodo na Mmekọrịta Obodo maka Lagos Steetiị.
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị na Ikeja Primary School
Ka oge na-aga, ọ kwagara Multi-Lateral Grammar School, Okun_Owa, Ogun State

Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ elemeṅtrị ya, ọ sonyeere Adeola Odutola College, Ijebu-Ode Ogun State secondary educational, ma mgbe ọ gụsịrị ya, a nabatara ya na Mahadum Ibadan, ebe ọ gụsịrịụsịrị akwụkwọ na Bachelor of Scieince n'afọ 1983
O nwetara nzere masta ya na Public Administration na Mahadum Lagos State n'afọ 2008.

Mgbe National Youth Service gasịrị, ọ malitere azụmahịa onwe ya na-arụ ọrụ na Accessories na Computers nke dugara ya n'ịtọlite azụmaahịa ndị ọzọ na-aga nke ọma nke gụnyere Compu-point Nigeria Limited, Data point Nigeria limited, Ipod Nigeria limited na Taseto Nigeria Limited nke bụ Chief Executive Officer. Arobieke na-eje ozi n'okpuru ọfịs ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, ọ bụ onye isi odeakwụkwọ mbụ nke Agboyi-Ketu LCDA na 2003, ma mesịa bụrụ onye isi oche mbụ nke Agbeyi-Keto LCDA n'ihe dị ka afọ 2004 na 2007

Ka ọ na-eje ozi na Lagos State, ṅa mbụ, a họpụtara ya dị ka Kọmishọna Honourable iji jee ozi na Ministry of Local Government and Community Affairs, ṅke Gọvanọ Sanwo-Olu họpụtara na 2019, na nso nso a, a kpọghachiri ya na Ministry of Wealth Creation and Employment na Jeṅụwarị, 2020. N'okpuru nchịkwa ya, ọ na-etinye usoro ọgbụgba na otu esi ewepụ enweghị ọrụ na Lagos State.
